<template>
  <el-cascader-panel class="panel" :options="options"/>
</template>

<script setup>
import axios from "axios";
import {ref} from "vue";

let options = ref([]);

axios.get('http://localhost:8080/chapterselect').then((response) => {
  options.value = response.data.data;
});



</script>


<style scoped>
.panel {
  width: fit-content;
  height: max-content;
}
</style>
